build/
# Drift fixtures must ship their pre-rendered build/ trees so they reproduce
# hermetically on fresh clones (CI included).
!tests/drift/*/build/
!tests/drift/*/build/**
*.local.*
.env
.env.*
secrets/
secrets.*.yaml
auth.json
.credentials*
**/sessions/
**/history/
**/cache/
.cache/
.private/
.claude/
backup-*.zip

# Override the user's global ignore so this repo can version its own
# repo-local agent policy. agent-runtime-kit is the source of truth for the
# runtime layer, so its AGENTS.md / CLAUDE.md must travel with the repo.
!AGENTS.md
!CLAUDE.md
